<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Verified · Yahao Translator</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC",
          "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e8eef5 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }

      .card {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        padding: 48px 40px;
        max-width: 460px;
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .icon {
        width: 72px;
        height: 72px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: #d1fae5;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin: 0 auto 24px;
      }

      .icon svg {
        width: 36px;
        height: 36px;
        stroke: #059669;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .lang-divider {
        margin: 24px 0;
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 32px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #2563eb;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="icon">
        <svg
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke-width="3"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
        >
          <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1>Email Verified</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Your email has been verified successfully.<br />You can now close this
        tab and return to the extension to sign in.
      </p>

      <hr class="lang-divider" />

      <h1>邮箱验证成功</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        您的邮箱已验证完成。<br />请关闭此页面，回到扩展中登录使用。
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        Yahao Translator ·
        <a href="https://yahaotranslate.com">yahaotranslate.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
